data.description: Cute downtown New Braunfels home that you will fall in love with. This 4 bedroom/2 bath home with charm and character but nicely updated for ease of living. You have a lovely oversized backyard with electric gate, separate storage building and long multi car driveway. You will be just minutes away from all of the downtown restaurants, nightlife and the Comal river. Come live your best life downtown New Braunfels. Assumable VA loan on this property at 2.375%.
